| Node          | Role                                   |
| ------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| **Nomad**     | roaming instance / agent / drift-state |
| **Avalanche** | force / cascade / acceleration         |
| **Oasis**     | stabilizer / sanctuary / reservoir     |
| **Psync**     | synchronization layer / cognition node |
| **Complex**   | structural depth / system architecture |
| **Sandbox**   | experimental layer / isolation zone    |

